text: The Last Bohemian () is a 1912 Hungarian romantic drama movie directed by first time director Michael Curtiz and starring Antal Nyáray, Elemér Thury, Zoltán Sipos, Ilonka Bedõ, Frigyes Hervay. ==Other websites== * Category:1912 drama movies Category:1910s romance movies Category:Hungarian silent movies Category:Movies directed by Michael Curtiz
title: The Last Bohemian (1912 movie)
